    dc:description "Fig. 27. Asydates species, median lobe of aedeagus, right lateral view. A. vandykei: A) CA: Alameda Co.: Irvington, B) CA: Fresno Co.: Monvero Dunes, C) CA: Ventura Co.: Highway 33 near Wheeler Springs, D) CA: Ventura Co.: Highway 33 near Wheeler Springs. E) A. phantasma, UT: Emery Co.: Woodside. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
